    "explanation": "Use AWS Snowball Edge Storage Optimized. Snowball Edge is ideal for large offline transfers (50 TB in 2 weeks) without VPN bottlenecks. DataSync (Option A) is for online transfers; Direct Connect (Option B) is too slow."
